Medi-Rx America Inc said its RxPlus Inc subsidiary received a letter of intent for a proposedinitial public offering of four mln dlrs to six mln dlrs.    It also said the subisidary, formed to franchise retaildrug stores, recently placed a 1.2 mln dlrs equity offeringwith private investors and secured a one mln dlrs line ofcredit for assisting applications for a Rx Plus franchise. Reuter&#3;